---
// NotJust.astro — Lightweight differentiator
---

<section class="notjust-section" style="padding: 80px clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px) 60px;">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title" data-reveal>See what happened.<br><em class="notjust-italic">Then do something about it.</em></h2>
    <div class="notjust-row" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
      <div class="notjust-card">
        <span class="notjust-label">Tracing tools</span>
        <span class="notjust-headline">Show you what happened.</span>
        <span class="notjust-detail">Which tools were called, how long it took, where it failed. But you can only watch.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="notjust-card">
        <span class="notjust-label">Durable execution engines</span>
        <span class="notjust-headline">Let you control it.</span>
        <span class="notjust-detail">Cancel, pause, resume, replay. But you need a separate runtime and a new SDK to get there.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="notjust-card notjust-kitaru">
        <span class="notjust-label">Kitaru</span>
        <span class="notjust-headline">Both. Just Python.</span>
        <span class="notjust-detail">Full control over running agents. Works with your existing tracing. <code>pip install kitaru</code> and two decorators.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .notjust-italic {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .notjust-headline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .notjust-detail {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .notjust-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .notjust-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface-warm);
  }

  .notjust-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .notjust-line {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .notjust-kitaru {
    border-color: rgba(241, 120, 41, 0.35);
    background: rgba(241, 120, 41, 0.06);
  }

  .notjust-kitaru .notjust-label {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .notjust-kitaru .notjust-line {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .notjust-line code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: rgba(241, 120, 41, 0.1);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .notjust-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
